file.name: getItem.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  '/items/{id}':
    get:
      summary: Get item by id
      description: Get item by id
      operationId: getItemById
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Item'
    parameters:
      - name: id
        in: path
        description: Id of the item
        required: true
        schema:
          type: string
          format: uuid
components:
  schemas:
    Item:
      title: Item
      description: A single item.
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          format: uuid
          example: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
        name:
          type: string
        number:
          type: number
